{"data":{"page":{"id":"a9183b0e-a98b-5606-bcd1-ff36f95158fa","html":"<p class=\"work-links\">\n<a class=\"btn icon icon-external\" href=\"http://work.joanmira.com/webs/nosurrender/\" target=\"_blank\">Launch archived website without DB</a>\n</p>\n<p>No Surrender contacted me to build an online shop to sell their products. They wanted a very personal style combined with great UX and an easy payment method.</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1000px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 34.9%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"1\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/877ff/1.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/d2504/1.jpg 500w,\n/static/3371ec26fad6b9ba0d8a617e9f25bc11/877ff/1.jpg 1000w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1000px) 100vw, 1000px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>I used TIENDAFlash, the software that I previously created for another customer that required a Flash online shop. TIENDAFlash is a Flash + PHP + MySQL solution that allows the maximum flexibility in the front-end and a very compatible and extended tech stack for the backend. It also features a custom CMS to add/edit/remove products, categories, photos and customers. I also implemented a credit/debit card payment gateway using the API from ServiRed (a very popular banking network in Spain).</p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1064px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.0187969924812%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"2\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/7dec8/2.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/b2694/2.jpg 500w,\n/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/041ab/2.jpg 1000w,\n/static/aeb1b92ab9eb5f611168c5e5293e6e2e/7dec8/2.jpg 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1064px) 100vw, 1064px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n    style=\"position: relative; display: block;  max-width: 1064px; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;\"\n  >\n    <span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n      style=\"padding-bottom: 70.0187969924812%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n    >\n      <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        style=\"width: 100%; height: 100%; margin: 0; vertical-align: middle; position: absolute; top: 0; left: 0; box-shadow: inset 0px 0px 0px 400px transparent;\"\n        alt=\"3\"\n        title=\"\"\n        src=\"/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/7dec8/3.jpg\"\n        srcset=\"/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/b2694/3.jpg 500w,\n/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/041ab/3.jpg 1000w,\n/static/9c679189c670fc44ebb7b819c923b65b/7dec8/3.jpg 1064w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 1064px) 100vw, 1064px\"\n      />\n    </span>\n  </span>\n  </p>\n<p>\n  <spa